contractible_space:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `exprℝ -/
/-- A non-empty convex set is a contractible space. -/
protected theorem convex.contractible_space (hs : convex (exprℝ) s) (hne : s.nonempty) : contractible_space s :=
  let ⟨x, hx⟩ := hne
  (hs.star_convex hx).contractible_space hne
#align convex.contractible_space convex.contractible_space
